00:06:56,641 --> 00:07:24,454
praise and blame you see we all like to be praised for what we do and when we don't get it we feel well we don't feel good it's worse of course if they blame see we had a meditator here just recently who seems to be in a real toxic atmosphere at work in IT everybody's blaming everybody he just finds it so difficult

70
00:07:25,244 --> 00:07:26,685
in a blame culture, you know.

71
