00:07:37,697 --> 00:07:39,800
When I was in Sri Lanka, there used to be this bird.

75
00:07:39,821 --> 00:07:41,322
I think it was a sea bird.

76
00:07:41,401 --> 00:07:42,362
I never actually saw it.

77
00:07:44,406 --> 00:07:46,367
Mainly because there were so many trees around.

78
00:07:46,867 --> 00:07:52,634
But as it flew over, it used to say, he did it, he did it.

