86
00:08:20,661 --> 00:08:50,549
and we're elated by it so we have to go into this meaning about elation and then of course when we're sick when we're ill when we don't feel when we can't eat and we want to eat and all that you just get dejected you're miserable see so you can see how it works now what does he mean you have to be careful here what does he mean by elated and dejected and then he goes on to say of course that the instructed person does not become elated right

87
00:08:51,052 --> 00:08:57,980
So you have to be very careful here because if you say to yourself, well this is a great meal, right?

