I feel miserable and the other thing is not to be afraid of pleasure just in case you indulge and then you get all the misery because that fear then stops you really enjoying things so when it comes to something that you say in advance that you know you're going to enjoy then it's just putting in that right intention just getting that right relationship so if if for instance great wealth comes to you you know because you you played the lottery or something

101
00:11:07,488 --> 00:11:36,937
heaven forbid you play that and you've got all these millions millions of pounds come your way so you know i mean that's that's great wealth now what would you do with it you see i mean what they say is that people who earn who get this enormous amount of money they are elated for one year and that's it then they get really and it goes back to ordinary horrible life see so it's a case of if wealth comes to us by whatever means

