I think everybody went, you know, I must be a fool, I must be an idiot, you know.

110
00:12:03,697 --> 00:12:10,104
And he said, I think it's something about, there's no point in me being happy if others around me aren't.

111
00:12:10,124 --> 00:12:11,785
It's something of that nature.

112
00:12:11,826 --> 00:12:14,328
