128
00:14:02,811 --> 00:14:04,653
And she says to me, will you make me a cup of tea?

129
00:14:06,375 --> 00:14:08,839
Oh no, I said, I said, would you like a cup of tea?

130
00:14:08,918 --> 00:14:10,240
She says, yes I would.

131
00:14:10,260 --> 00:14:11,341
Make it very weak, she said.

132
00:14:11,942 --> 00:14:12,604
I said, okay.

133
00:14:12,624 --> 00:14:13,184
So I went out.

134
00:14:14,346 --> 00:14:15,668
