137
00:14:22,998 --> 00:14:26,903
And she was really upset, so I took it out and made another one.

138
00:14:27,371 --> 00:14:29,073
It's too strong, oh my goodness.

139
00:14:29,094 --> 00:14:36,341
She had this sort of, whatever she meant by weak, I never really figured out.

140
00:14:37,042 --> 00:14:41,527
