say thank you very much and very quietly say to yourself any moment this could be broken this could break and when it breaks you just say oh look it's broken see what's the problem see it's the same way it's the same way you know you buy something like I don't know one of these iPhones I mean they cost a bit you know you see and you buy one and then you say this could disappear this could be stolen you see so

